        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li class="hover:text-primary transition-all transform hover:translate-x-2">
            <a href="tel:+573146755310">+57 314 6755310</a>
          </li>
          <li class="hover:text-primary transition-all transform hover:translate-x-2">
            <a href="mailto:ac.arteconstructivo@gmail.com">ac.arteconstructivo@gmail.com</a>
